- Search DB, store, analyse and correlate logs from disparate application and systems.
- Need to run on servers
- Usecase:
  1) Log Analytics
  2) Real ttime application monitoring
  3) Security Analytics
  4) FTS
  5) Click stream Analytics
  6) Indexing

- Elastic search + Kibana + Logstash:
  - Elastic search provides search and indexing capability 
  - Kibana will give realtime dashboard of data that sits on ES
  - Logstash: uses logstash agent, log ingestion mechnism